core.game

Class GameDescription

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.game.GameDescription

  • public class GameDescription
extends java.lang.Object
    This is an abstract class encapsulating all the data required for generating and testing game levels.
    Author:
    Ahmed A Khalifa
